Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:11.28,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:15.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:22.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:26.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.53,0:00:30.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:33.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:36.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:40.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.15,0:00:44.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:48.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:50.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:54.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:59.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:02.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.72,0:01:11.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:15.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:18.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.91,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,160.389)}The Monstrous Elekibotaru's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.91,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs175\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,700.389)}Fireball Attack!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Elekibotaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.52,0:01:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to show your potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.61,0:01:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You must use your power\Nto reduce Japan to ruin,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.78,0:01:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,so that we may erect a Shocker Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be the final charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, I give you life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.09,0:02:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Naoki! Get your head up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.27,0:02:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.12,0:02:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep kicking your legs!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Look alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How did I look, Coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a long way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.60,0:02:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.84,0:02:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Another power outage?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Rise, Elekibotaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Steal all of Tokyo's electricity,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and become the deadly Elekibotaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that light?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's check it out.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it came from around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a firefly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.07,0:04:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.20,0:04:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Fireflies don't grow that big...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit eerie, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We should really go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shine! Fly! Dance the dance of madness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shine! Fly! Dance the dance of madness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now inflict my hypnosis\Nupon these foolish humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't... I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like my electric hypnosis?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'll kill you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This electric fire will burn you to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Hongo Takeshi,\Nso I won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a greater purpose for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My dance of hell will make you my slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:06:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You must destroy Hongo, enemy of Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.81,0:06:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,These are friends of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.88,0:06:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if they\Ncould join the Racing Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yokko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Choco.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the club Chairman,\NMr. Hongo, and Mr. Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.56,0:06:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going to show them around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sure.\N- Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.21,0:06:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The power outage yesterday\Nwas completely unexplained.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It said enough electricity\Nwas diverted in an instant
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to power Tokyo for ten days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten days?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it. The firefly monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:06:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker is behind it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true, Naoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Next to the third sluice\Ngate of the Tama River.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We should investigate, anyhow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, be careful, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll look this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing out of the ordinary here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But who but Shocker could\Ndo something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be a clue somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.80,0:08:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it was really a Shocker\Nmonster that Naoki saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.33,0:08:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What else could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But then... why didn't\Nhe come to us last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hongo. What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It suggests a considerable\Ndischarge of electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.65,0:08:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.81,0:08:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come, Hongo! Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.21,0:09:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.59,0:09:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You walked right into my trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a Shocker cyborg?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Elekibotaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Elekibotaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.51,0:09:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.17,0:10:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Elekibotaru,\Nwe'll finish this another time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you running from me, Rider?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that, Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I'm fine. It's just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We should focus on\Nfinding their base instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be hasty, Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The real problem is\NElekibotaru's electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to contain unimaginable power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way we can win is if we\Nfigure out how to steal that from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you let Hongo escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker does not suffer failures.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.02,0:11:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I will defeat Hongo next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already taken our next steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo and Mr. Taki\Nhave been out a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Naoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You look down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And grouchy, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shucks. He hasn't said\Na word to me all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Think he's sick or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:12:01.61,Italics,,0,0,0,,Naoki, do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:03.66,Italics,,0,0,0,,Attack your comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Naoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.14,0:12:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, knock it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki's acting strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.10,0:12:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:48.74,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- Pops!\N- Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri and the girls... kidnapped by Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:31.49,Italics,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:35.61,Italics,,0,0,0,,The electricity in his body was grounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a stake and a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, I need a stake and a rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.28,0:13:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Meet up with me later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The third sluice gate on the Tama River.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.95,0:13:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:13:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.08,0:14:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, I think it's that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our club badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.35,0:14:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew we'd find something here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.12,0:14:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that be it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You have an important task ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo and Taki will soon\Ncome here to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But when they do come, they will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, this must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It definitely looks like\NShocker architecture...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.61,0:16:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for you, Hongo, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've prepared a grave just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You've met your end at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki. Take the others and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak to me, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, speak to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Elekibotaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Show them your dance of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.70,0:17:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dance of hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo... watch closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,0:17:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill Hongo and Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight them! Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.07,0:17:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They've all been hypnotized!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them! Give them all you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.98,0:17:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this, Yokko, Mitsuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, we can't afford to harm them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:17:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use, Taki.\NWe have to knock them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.42,0:18:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel the wrath of my electric fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.43,0:20:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! I brought it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.79,0:20:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.49,0:20:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.05,0:21:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Elekibotaru,\NI will steal your electricity!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're finished now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.53,0:22:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Throw!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:14.59,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:17.65,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.14,0:20:21.70,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:25.20,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.23,0:20:28.85,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:32.48,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:35.00,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.05,0:20:38.46,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:43.26,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:46.72,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.83,0:20:57.52,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:21:00.45,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.06,0:21:04.61,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:08.20,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:12.08,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:15.12,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.64,0:21:18.13,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:21.65,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.62,0:21:26.22,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:29.76,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.03,0:21:40.53,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.53,0:21:43.52,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:47.87,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.87,0:21:51.39,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.40,0:21:54.96,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.97,0:21:57.83,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.53,0:22:01.26,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:05.00,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.81,0:22:09.42,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.42,0:22:13.11,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.69,0:22:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What were we...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.54,0:22:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're okay now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.42,0:22:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's go.\N- Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.71,0:22:59.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Once again, Kamen Rider was able to\Ndefeat the terrifying killer Elekibotaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.01,0:23:02.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker would surely\Nsend a new cyborg soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:04.39,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ride on, Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.39,0:23:06.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Fight, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:10.68,Cont,,0,50,160,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:13.33,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(290.175,252.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.53,0:23:14.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next week is the first episode\Nof an amazing location shoot series.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.13,0:23:16.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Set on Mount Rokko in Arima, Kobe,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.08,0:23:18.83,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Rider pursues the Mexican\Nmonster Abugomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.83,0:23:23.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The action on the Rokko Ropeway\Nsuspended 130 meters in the air
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.18,0:23:24.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,will prove especially thrilling.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.64,0:23:28.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for "The Mount Rokko\NPursuit of the Monstrous Abugomes!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.21,0:23:30.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's going to be amazing!\NBe sure to tune in!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.28,0:23:30.88,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs105\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(487.167,717.389)}The Mount Rokko Pursuit of\N the Monstrous Abugomes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:40.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.25,0:23:43.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.30,0:23:45.12,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.12,0:23:48.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the villains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.77,0:23:50.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.60,0:23:52.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.52,0:23:54.29,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.29,0:23:55.91,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.08,0:23:58.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.20,0:24:03.91,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with all of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.91,0:24:07.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.46,0:24:11.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.55,0:24:15.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous Elekibotaru's\NFireball Attack!!